text: Orphic Signs is the second studio album by the technical death metal band Desecravity. It was released on November 15 of 2014 on Willowtip Records. == Track listing == ==Credits== * Yuichi Kudo - Drums * Daisuke Ichiboshi - Bass * Shogo Tokita - Vocals/guitars Category:2014 albums Category:Desecravity albums
